{"id": 605, "genre": 1001, "title": "你为什么爱美剧？", "description": "就爱看哈哈哈，睡睡睡，非常朴实的一项爱好。", "record_count": 10918, "comment_count": 0, "praise_count": 0, "image": "img/paper/paper_show/20160606145100wQJ9P6CINyKsie0d.jpg", "page_style": 0, "category": 2, "column": 2, "type": "paper", "date": "2015-11-03T10:37:18Z", "options": [{"id": 22528, "content": "拍的好", "image": "img/option/option/201606052115071sC4oG9V0zYiIdTA.jpg", "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 287085}, {"id": 22017, "content": "FBI各种间谍 炒鸡爱！", "image": null, "praise_count": 1, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 134430}, {"id": 23303, "content": "题材丰富。 涉及真实社会事件。 敢自嘲。 不拖拉。 有智商。 说脱就脱。 ", "image": null, "praise_count": 2, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 130596}, {"id": 22281, "content": "美女帅哥，各种狗血各种血腥各种乱睡各种boss各种不可能的可能等等", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 285537}, {"id": 22285, "content": "女主男主会睡别人的……", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 234652}, {"id": 22287, "content": "没啥理由，和我看日剧和韩剧的原因一样，总觉得国内电视剧离不开那些婆婆妈妈的关系，家庭伦理剧实在欣赏不来。", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 285639}, {"id": 24849, "content": "因为剧尊重每一个角色。即便没有露几次脸的小角色他们都有自己的人格。", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 304163}, {"id": 23318, "content": "可以笑出腹肌", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 291740}, {"id": 41239, "content": "电视剧不是连续剧", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 422646}, {"id": 23066, "content": "库布里克的电视剧", "image": null, "praise_count": 1, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 290315}, {"id": 21787, "content": "剧情不拖沓不啰嗦", "image": null, "praise_count": 1187, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 280853}, {"id": 21788, "content": "特点鲜明，该科幻够科幻，该血腥也够血腥，至于h嘛…", "image": null, "praise_count": 1134, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 216032}, {"id": 21789, "content": "猜不透！", "image": null, "praise_count": 242, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 134885}, {"id": 22045, "content": "中国的能看？", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 267817}, {"id": 21790, "content": "烧脑", "image": null, "praise_count": 421, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 213061}, {"id": 22814, "content": "不用被脑残导演侮辱智商就是好", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 211187}, {"id": 21791, "content": "学英语？", "image": null, "praise_count": 236, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 160835}, {"id": 24607, "content": "红色+黄色", "image": null, "praise_count": 1, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 301961}, {"id": 21792, "content": "起码不是婆媳问题的题材", "image": null, "praise_count": 895, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 259825}, {"id": 22048, "content": "所有细节一丝不苟，没有粗制滥造，题材很广，什么都可以涉猎，演的逼真到位", "image": null, "praise_count": 1, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 283814}, {"id": 21793, "content": "敢撕", "image": null, "praise_count": 133, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 145609}, {"id": 25633, "content": "练听力?", "image": "img/option/option/20160605211622U0LiD7GfpTAWXe5y.jpg", "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 308208}, {"id": 42273, "content": "没有傻白甜", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 429564}, {"id": 21794, "content": "感觉美剧特点鲜明吧。国产剧放眼看去不是手撕鬼子神仙谈恋爱就是后宫娘娘撕逼大战（当然不乏好剧，观点有失偏颇莫怪）。但是看美剧的时候感觉总能找到自己感兴趣的类型，种类繁多，特点也很鲜明。", "image": null, "praise_count": 580, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 281303}, {"id": 23331, "content": "感觉会提高我的智商", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 289289}, {"id": 21796, "content": "不然看国内的吗？总要看一个", "image": null, "praise_count": 67, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 279465}, {"id": 23333, "content": "主要有XXOO看", "image": "img/option/option/20160605211521qiWpkQvSA5BKbhtf.jpg", "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 291809}, {"id": 21798, "content": "漏的多……吧……", "image": null, "praise_count": 20, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 179916}, {"id": 22054, "content": "不爱的人可以说话吗", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 236360}, {"id": 21799, "content": "剧本很好，演员演技水平普遍较高", "image": null, "praise_count": 640, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 250401}, {"id": 21800, "content": "说裸就裸，毫不忸怩", "image": null, "praise_count": 703, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 2557}, {"id": 21801, "content": "因为美国电影质量下降厉害，多出的时间看美剧。", "image": null, "praise_count": 16, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 281717}, {"id": 21803, "content": "精彩的剧情！看美剧不用快进！", "image": null, "praise_count": 525, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 96631}, {"id": 45611, "content": "类型丰富", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 450692}, {"id": 21804, "content": "因为没广告", "image": null, "praise_count": 120, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 268549}, {"id": 21805, "content": "好看", "image": null, "praise_count": 36, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 159579}, {"id": 22573, "content": "因为Sheldon", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 287279}, {"id": 21806, "content": "学英语！而且美剧不啰嗦，最重要喜欢美剧的男主女主啊都是男神女神！！而且剧情比较适合现在的我们哈哈哈哈", "image": null, "praise_count": 60, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 276894}, {"id": 21807, "content": "肉欲，烧脑，节奏快", "image": null, "praise_count": 89, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 281729}, {"id": 21808, "content": "国产剧里广告打得太僵硬。台词太白话。", "image": null, "praise_count": 102, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 187946}, {"id": 22576, "content": "真实的害怕，夸张的惊悚", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 105821}, {"id": 21809, "content": "我到现在还不知道我男主死了没←_←", "image": "img/option/option/20160702200753FYAoNPWImp6JMxe8.jpg", "praise_count": 66, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 278522}, {"id": 22833, "content": "哈哈哈哈哈", "image": null, "praise_count": 1, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 289069}, {"id": 21810, "content": "有说的就说，没说的就结束，痛快！有黄有暴力，但是就是恰到好处", "image": null, "praise_count": 207, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 220175}, {"id": 22066, "content": "喜剧笑点高 悬疑剧水平高 恐怖剧吓点高", "image": null, "praise_count": 5, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 200853}, {"id": 22578, "content": "信息量大，一集美剧的信息量堪比一部电影。", "image": null, "praise_count": 1, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 167396}, {"id": 31794, "content": "节奏紧凑，顺便为了练听力", "image": null, "praise_count": 1, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 340520}, {"id": 21811, "content": "演的不假", "image": null, "praise_count": 64, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 277815}, {"id": 23347, "content": "45分钟结束一个故事。简单粗暴。", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 291856}, {"id": 21812, "content": "就是喜欢", "image": null, "praise_count": 25, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 252201}]}